  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Part of a valid long sum 8.12345678901234567 is hidden beyond the screen edges in Specify amount:\r\n![screenshot_20170629-163130](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/27690206-5b4622da-5ce9-11e7-819f-62c6040328bc.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nfull sum even if it's long one is completely visible\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nPart of a long sum 8.12345678901234567 is hidden beyond the screen edges, figures 8 and 5 are not visible\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- in 1-1 chat send someone 8.12345678901234567\r\n- check that it can be fully visible under Specify amount \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: send PR build, 0.9.8-53-gc74838e+\r\n* Operating System: iOS and Android",
